{#
You Are Here:
- Archive for Ghostwind
- src/site/_themes/ghostwind/archive.njk

How It Works:
- On build, this page adds a postslist of
  1. src/site/blog
  2. src/site/video
  3. src/site/blog AND src/site/video

Dynamic Data:
- anything in {{ curly braces }} is a variable from:
  (a) frontmatter in the associated markdown file (src/site/page/blog.md,
      src/site/page/video.md, src/site/page/archive.md)
  (b) src/site/_globals
- aliases are defined in `{% set %}`
#}
